  "A stratified sample of voters": "",
  "A sample of 1,000 people": "",
  "A type of cluster sample": "",
  "A study that collects data from every member of the population": "",
  "A census attempts to gather information from every individual in the entire population rather than from a sample.": "",
  "What does 'sampling variability' mean?": "",
  "All samples give exactly the same result": "",
  "Different random samples from the same population produce different estimates": "",
